<!-- Javascript history : -->
Javascript is a object -oriented programming language.which is used by developers for client side as welll as server
side scripting.

this is a scripting language that is used to create and control dynamic website content.

It is a powerfull scriptigng language which gets executed from top to bottom works

The difference between javascript and other programming languages is that javascript code gets compiled in runtime ,
unlike other languages which explicitely compile the code and then execute separately

Javascript is not a compiled language but it is translated language , that means the code gets translated in the browser
that the time of execution . The translater for this code comes in-built in the browser .

History :
Developed in 1995 by Brendon Eich in just 10 days in Netscape communication 
It was initially called mocha, then livescript and final javascript. The name java was included only for marketing purpose

It was later handle over to ECMA (European Computer Manufacturer Assosiation) which standardized javascript under ECMA-262.

<!-- General Features : -->
- Structured Programming language just like C.
- It is a weakly types/Dynamic/Loosely typed language.
- It is a light-weighted (Taking less RAM)and interpreted language(runtime )
- It is a case-sensitive language.
- It is a client-side scripting language.
- It is a platform-independent language.(It can run on any OS)
- It provides users with good control over the browser.

<!-- Java vs Javascript : -->
 Java :
 - Java is class based language.
 - Java is a multi-threaded language 
 - It consumed more memory as compared to javascript
 - Class Based
 - Compiled language 
 - Java is used to build standalone app, and enterprise level app. 



Javascript :
- is a event based language that means it can be triggered by events like onclick, onmouseover, onsubmit etc.
- Javascript is a single threaded language 
- It consumes less memory as compared to java
- Object based 
- interpreted language
- It is used to build web app, Mobile app , etc

